      <title>地震后曼谷大楼倒塌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-29/bangkok-building-collapses-after-earthquake-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在发生7.7级地震和余震6.4的余震之后，建筑物在曼谷的Chatuchak区倒塌。周五，地震震撼了缅甸和附近的泰国，摧毁了建筑物，桥梁和水坝。  （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-29/bangkok-building-collapses-after-earthquake-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 16:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国地震后的第一响应者清除瓦砾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-29/first-responders-clear-rubble-after-thailand-earthquake-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[救援工作一直持续到曼谷的夜晚，以清除瓦砾，并从周五袭击泰国和邻近缅甸的强大地震中救出任何幸存者。随着瓦砾从瓦砾中拉出更多的尸体，缅甸地震的死亡人数已跃升至1,600多个。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-29/first-responders-clear-rubble-after-thailand-earthquake-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 16:21:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
