      <title>随着外国救援队的到来，缅甸地震收费达到1,644</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/myanmar-quake-death-toll-surges-as-thai-rescuers-continue-search</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于国际救援队的到来，缅甸在周五强大的地震中的死亡人数在第二大曼德勒市的巨大破坏中达到了1,644次，以帮助寻找幸存者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-29/myanmar-quake-death-toll-surges-as-thai-rescuers-continue-search</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Mar 2025 04:04:31 GMT</pubDate>
